    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Made by Elwin</h2>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>This is a special feature that can only be triggered by the <em>Spirit Shield</em> feature.<br />\n  When used, it will damage the attacker that triggered the <em>Spirit Shield</em> by the amount of damage that was prevented from the target.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature needs to be triggered by Spirit Shield (found in MISC Class Features) to work properly.</p>",
      "chat": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">When you use your Spirit Shield to reduce the damage of an attack, the attacker takes an amount of force damage equal to the damage that your Spirit Shield prevents.</span></p>"
